'''法拉第波'''（{{lang-en|Faraday waves}} 或 {{lang|en|Faraday ripples}}），以[[麥可·法拉第|麥可·法拉第]]（{{lang|en|Michael Faraday}}）為名，是一種振盪容器中液面的[[非線性|非線性]][[駐波|駐波]]，當其振盪頻率超過臨界值時，平靜液面就會開始不穩，這現象稱之為法拉第[[不穩定性|不穩性]]。法拉第最早是在1831年[[皇家學會|皇家學會]]《[[自然科学会报|自然科学会报]]》裡的一篇文章附錄中提到法拉第波<ref>Faraday, M. (1831) "On a peculiar class of acoustical figures; and on certain forms assumed by a group of particles upon vibrating elastic surfaces", ''Philosophical Transactions of the Royal Society (London)'', vol. 121, pages 299–318.  "Faraday waves" are discussed in an appendix to the article, [https://books.google.com/books?id=RgOc86j3VTwC&pg=PA335&lpg=PA335&source=bl&ots=2tJKmzwP3j&sig=HZfgsPbHFffKkZdzy_QZu8w3v8s&hl=en&ei=d1UWTPHvB8O78gaR4PSwCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&f=false "On the forms and states assumed by fluids in contact with vibrating elastic surfaces"] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RgOc86j3VTwC&pg=PA335&lpg=PA335&source=bl&ots=2tJKmzwP3j&sig=HZfgsPbHFffKkZdzy_QZu8w3v8s&hl=en&ei=d1UWTPHvB8O78gaR4PSwCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBUQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&f=false |date=20190812140459 }}.  This entire article is also available on-line (albeit without illustrations) at [http://www.ebooksread.com/authors-eng/michael-faraday/experimental-researches-in-chemistry-and-physics-hci/page-31-experimental-researches-in-chemistry-and-physics-hci.shtml "Electronic Library"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ebooksread.com/authors-eng/michael-faraday/experimental-researches-in-chemistry-and-physics-hci/page-31-experimental-researches-in-chemistry-and-physics-hci.shtml |date=20190917072034 }}.</ref><ref>Others who investigated "Faraday waves" include:  '''(1)'''  Ludwig Matthiessen (1868) [https://books.google.com/books?id=jQs4AAAAMAAJ&pg=PA107&lpg=PA107&source=bl&ots=eac7KB3ZIo&sig=VQJ-cz4g5haOkpNugwPNMMURzuM&hl=en&ei=82IWTKeoB8H78Abek6ieDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false "Akustische Versuche, die kleinsten Transversalwellen der Flüssigkeiten betreffend" (Acoustic experiments concerning the smallest transverse waves of liquids)] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jQs4AAAAMAAJ&pg=PA107&lpg=PA107&source=bl&ots=eac7KB3ZIo&sig=VQJ-cz4g5haOkpNugwPNMMURzuM&hl=en&ei=82IWTKeoB8H78Abek6ieDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBQQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20190813071837 }}, ''Annalen der Physik'', vol. 134, pages 107–117 ; '''(2)'''  Ludwig Matthiessen (1870) [https://books.google.com/books?id=82_kAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA375&lpg=PA375&source=bl&ots=iuyi1V7XpL&sig=AFlaE433VRg-I60K1xyWx734PS4&hl=en&ei=qF8WTLTqN4L58AbpnuirCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CBwQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false "Über die Transversalschwingungen tönender tropfbarer und elastischer Flüssigkeiten" (On the transverse vibrations of ringing low-viscosity and elastic liquids)] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=82_kAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA375&lpg=PA375&source=bl&ots=iuyi1V7XpL&sig=AFlaE433VRg-I60K1xyWx734PS4&hl=en&ei=qF8WTLTqN4L58AbpnuirCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CBwQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20190815143039 }}, ''Annalen der Physik'', vol. 141, pages 375–393 ; '''(3)'''  John William Strutt (Lord Rayleigh) (1883), [https://books.google.com/books?id=GFMbAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA50&lpg=PA50&source=bl&ots=qQRs8BFx9D&sig=wKvFicJrCCL4k-q_0ScjoP7pW-I&hl=en&ei=NmIWTLCdD4P88AaOtOinCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBIQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&f=false "On the crispations of fluid resting upon a vibrating support,"] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GFMbAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA50&lpg=PA50&source=bl&ots=qQRs8BFx9D&sig=wKvFicJrCCL4k-q_0ScjoP7pW-I&hl=en&ei=NmIWTLCdD4P88AaOtOinCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CBIQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&f=false |date=20190813012011 }} ''Philosophical Magazine'', vol. 16, pages 50–58.</ref>。

若將一層液體放置在垂直振蕩的活塞頂部，在特定的不穩性條件下，會出現以一半活塞頻率振盪的[[駐波|駐波]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Patterning of particulate films using Faraday waves|author=Wright, P.H.; Saylor, J.R. (September 2003)|url=http://www.ces.clemson.edu/~jsaylor/paperPdfs/rsi.v74.n09.pdf|journal=Review of Scientific Instruments. 74 (9): 4063–4070|issue=|doi=|others=|year=|volume=|page=|pmid=|access-date=2017-04-19|archive-date=2010-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609161604/http://www.ces.clemson.edu/~jsaylor/paperPdfs/rsi.v74.n09.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 這與 [[參數振盪器|參數共振]]問題有關。駐波形式可能會是條紋、緊密堆積[[六邊形|六邊形]]、甚至是[[正方形|正方形]]或[[準晶體|準週期]]。常在發出鈴鐺聲的葡萄酒酒杯內的葡萄酒表面，觀察到細條紋的法拉第波。 法拉第波也能解釋佛教法器「[[磬_(法器)|磬]]」裡的噴泉現象。

法拉第波及其波長，可以用[[量子力學|量子力學]]裡[[德布羅意-玻姆理論|德布羅意-玻姆理論]]的[[物質波|德布羅意波]]及其波長來類比<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tcm.phy.cam.ac.uk/~mdt26/tti_talks/deBB_10/bush_tti2010.pdf|title=Quantum mechanics writ large|accessdate=|author=John W. M. Bush Department of Mathematics, MIT|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2017-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215051636/http://www.tcm.phy.cam.ac.uk/~mdt26/tti_talks/deBB_10/bush_tti2010.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 應用 ==
[[File:Assembly_of_microscale_beads_on_Faraday_waves.gif|微珠在法拉第波上聚集成團<ref name=":0" />]]
法拉第波可作為液體模板，用來引導聚集微小物質，包括[[軟物質|軟物質]]、[[剛體|剛體]]、生物實體(如單一細胞、細胞球體和種有細胞的微珠)。<ref name=":0" />與固體模板不同，液體模板可以通過調整振動頻率和加速度來動態調整，生成各種具對稱性及週期性的圖案。

這種現象也被鱷魚用來吸引配偶。它們會在略低水面處以低頻振動肺部，導致身上的尖刺移動並引發表面波。這些表面波基本上是法拉第波，可以觀察到特定共振造成的飛濺效應。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Horny Male Alligators Bellow With Their Back Spikes|url=https://www.wired.com/2011/05/alligator-mating-physics/|first1=Devin|date=2011-05-25|journal=Wired|accessdate=4 May 2016|last1=Powell|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217192104/https://www.wired.com/2011/05/alligator-mating-physics/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Faraday waves produced by periodic substrates: Mimicking the alligator water dance|first1=Peter|last2=Holt|first2=R. Glynn|date=2011|journal=The Journal of the Acoustical Society of America|issue=4|doi=10.1121/1.3587858|volume=129|pages=2411|bibcode=2011ASAJ..129.2411M|last1=Moriarty}}</ref>

